and tapped out the digits on his calculator 1957 
in jiddah a luggage merchant who asked to be called only hamid 
was packing up in bags from his own shop 
saudis and yemenis have always been like this he said 
interlocking his fingers why are we suddenly thrown out like 
enemies 
