alternative for people who can no longer handle jogging or team 
sports 
he warns though that prospective hikers should get a complete 
checkup before putting the extra stress on the cardiovascular 
system 
hixson by the way said most people would be amazed by the 
number of older people climbing the adirondacks 
older hikers run into the least trouble on the trails because 
they generally bring a lifetime of experience with them most 
older people who hike have hiked all their lives he said 
