weve seen a moderate increase over last years sales 
halloween seems to be selling well said beige although he 
declined to release sales figures 
hallmark said its stores are devoting the same amount of space 
to halloween merchandise this year as they did last year 
people put an emphasis on entertainment theyre not willing 
to sacrifice entertainment for themselves said philip morris 
president of morris costumes in charlotte nc which distributes 
