patrick 47 insurance 
separately two current executive vice presidents will head new 
support divisions they are jerome kenney 49 corporate strategy 
and research and herbert allison jr 47 finance and 
administration 
all will also serve on the firms executive management 
committee 
the new structure elevates key strategic ares of opportunity 
further streamlines the organization and elevates the role of our 
core line managers in directing business strategies and contolling 
costs said merrill chairman and chief executive william schreyer 
