says the foundation a summitarranged budget has never even 
reduced the deficit below the level of the summit year 
in short dont expect freedom day to occur much earlier next 
year the 1990 cost of running congress itself rose 106 percent 
over 1989 bringing the price tax to 23 billion thats the 
trend 
